{"tid":993954,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"裸辭去旅行(2)之東南亞篇[柬埔寨]","createTime":"2019-01-24T10:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T04:13:49.000Z","uid":231598,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0815ec770ac89c5425f2860ef56363f3672c7a2a","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"序：<br />\n是咁的。<br />\n小弟剛出黎做左野幾年，<br />\n喺啱啱夠資格去見board之際，<br />\n突然覺得好厭倦咁平凡嘅生活，<br />\n亦唔想一生就咁枉過，<br />\n返工、賺錢、結婚、生仔、死亡，<br />\n當你六七十歲望返轉頭嘅時候，<br />\n只想問一句：<br />\n究竟我呢幾十年做左啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n我辭左份算係高薪厚職嘅工，<br />\n打算轉工。<br />\n又會咁啱，<br />\n我未婚妻又有同一個念頭，<br />\n之後我地就一齊辭職。<br />\n<br />\n千載難逢嘅機會，<br />\n造就左我地今次為期大半年嘅渡蜜月。<br />\n<br />\n上一篇係越南篇，有興趣可以睇番：<br />\n東南亞五國之旅（處女post）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/983834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/983834</a><br />\n<br />\n琴日剛由胡志明坐巴士去左金邊，<br />\n去左個由學校轉型成為集中營嘅地方，<br />\n晏少少會詳細講下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zeqXbS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzeqXbS2.png&h=2710b051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎緊三日會去吳哥窟，<br />\n有興趣嘅巴絲們可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟都幾中意影相，<br />\n所以啲遊記都會多圖，<br />\n希望大家支持下"},{"pid":"ffb195446e62e27b7b18f6bcb3732fcb7f9ac918","tid":993954,"uid":151436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b18048e2dc569b04d39f3ef9990d982eb4ec989","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Day 1 胡志明 -&gt; 金邊</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[ part 1 ]</span><br />\n<br />\n終於可以離開呢個充滿電單車嘅國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ch4tkze.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCh4tkze.png&h=cc5e53c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMORikW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMORikW.png&h=bf286e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地真係好_煩<br />\n過每一條馬路都令我好攰好攰<br />\n喺馬路都算啦係應該我避你地嘅<br />\n但點解你地要連行人路都唔放過<br />\n你地係咪想迫死我地<br />\n<br />\n今日買左去金邊嘅車飛<br />\n格過價最平大概10USD/230000VND<br />\n大概80蚊，比想像中貴<br />\n呢間叫Kumho，架車都ok<br />\n個司機同個助手都幾nice<br />\n <br />\n成日聽喺柬埔寨過關嗰陣<br />\n啲海關會1蚊1蚊美金咁收你<br />\n係啲下欄錢<br />\n本身整個Visa要30USD（落地簽）<br />\n加埋兩三蚊小費就~33蚊<br />\n但如果你俾司機幫你整，就收你35蚊<br />\n（當然嗰5蚊係袋落自己袋）<br />\n<br />\n本身諗住成車4x人，我地跟大隊<br />\n希望有人可以一齊扺抗司機嘅威迫<br />\n點知，成架車坐得10條友<br />\n個個都乖乖地俾個passport個助手搞<br />\n咁我地可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明知人屈你錢但你咩都做唔到嗰下<br />\n真係好Sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fa2ywBo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffa2ywBo.png&h=1f1eb818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條日本仔<br />\n好似扮聽唔明佢講乜<br />\n之後逃過一劫<br />\n<br />\n胡志明去金邊個陸路關口，叫Bavet<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Hv8kvt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Hv8kvt.png&h=1157110b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知痴乜線<br />\n我竟然夠膽拎部手機出黎影個關口<br />\n好彩冇俾人捉入房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYtRihf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYtRihf.png&h=0f8f13cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身好驚俾完35蚊之後<br />\n又俾海關收多2-3蚊小費<br />\n好彩最後冇事，鬆一口氣<br />\n<br />\n過關嗰陣有人sell sim卡（冇鋪位嗰啲）<br />\n我心諗十幾蚊港紙上唔到咪當跌左<br />\n點知真係上唔到<br />\nsend個wtsapp msg要幾分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uJkwiiD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuJkwiiD.png&h=3f01cd47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過左關再搭多兩個幾鐘車就到金邊<br />\n一落車call左grab tuktuk<br />\n就去左酒店<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KP6n9ra.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKP6n9ra.png&h=806c8bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再徒步行兩三公里，<br />\n趕喺S21集中營閂門之前入去。"},{"pid":"da3729915084c7ed8443ed930a567a19a89e8500","tid":993954,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b18048e2dc569b04d39f3ef9990d982eb4ec989","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Day 1 胡志明 -&gt; 金邊</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[ part 1 ]</span><br />\n<br />\n終於可以離開呢個充滿電單車嘅國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ch4tkze.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCh4tkze.png&h=cc5e53c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMORikW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMORikW.png&h=bf286e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地真係好_煩<br />\n過每一條馬路都令我好攰好攰<br />\n喺馬路都算啦係應該我避你地嘅<br />\n但點解你地要連行人路都唔放過<br />\n你地係咪想迫死我地<br />\n<br />\n今日買左去金邊嘅車飛<br />\n格過價最平大概10USD/230000VND<br />\n大概80蚊，比想像中貴<br />\n呢間叫Kumho，架車都ok<br />\n個司機同個助手都幾nice<br />\n <br />\n成日聽喺柬埔寨過關嗰陣<br />\n啲海關會1蚊1蚊美金咁收你<br />\n係啲下欄錢<br />\n本身整個Visa要30USD（落地簽）<br />\n加埋兩三蚊小費就~33蚊<br />\n但如果你俾司機幫你整，就收你35蚊<br />\n（當然嗰5蚊係袋落自己袋）<br />\n<br />\n本身諗住成車4x人，我地跟大隊<br />\n希望有人可以一齊扺抗司機嘅威迫<br />\n點知，成架車坐得10條友<br />\n個個都乖乖地俾個passport個助手搞<br />\n咁我地可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明知人屈你錢但你咩都做唔到嗰下<br />\n真係好Sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fa2ywBo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffa2ywBo.png&h=1f1eb818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條日本仔<br />\n好似扮聽唔明佢講乜<br />\n之後逃過一劫<br />\n<br />\n胡志明去金邊個陸路關口，叫Bavet<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Hv8kvt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Hv8kvt.png&h=1157110b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知痴乜線<br />\n我竟然夠膽拎部手機出黎影個關口<br />\n好彩冇俾人捉入房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYtRihf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYtRihf.png&h=0f8f13cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身好驚俾完35蚊之後<br />\n又俾海關收多2-3蚊小費<br />\n好彩最後冇事，鬆一口氣<br />\n<br />\n過關嗰陣有人sell sim卡（冇鋪位嗰啲）<br />\n我心諗十幾蚊港紙上唔到咪當跌左<br />\n點知真係上唔到<br />\nsend個wtsapp msg要幾分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uJkwiiD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuJkwiiD.png&h=3f01cd47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過左關再搭多兩個幾鐘車就到金邊<br />\n一落車call左grab tuktuk<br />\n就去左酒店<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KP6n9ra.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKP6n9ra.png&h=806c8bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再徒步行兩三公里，<br />\n趕喺S21集中營閂門之前入去。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T22:27:08.000Z","msg":"佢地上網係好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a50e9a51db6934bbcb98a9b356c320638d494cc","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da3729915084c7ed8443ed930a567a19a89e8500","tid":993954,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b18048e2dc569b04d39f3ef9990d982eb4ec989","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Day 1 胡志明 -&gt; 金邊</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[ part 1 ]</span><br />\n<br />\n終於可以離開呢個充滿電單車嘅國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ch4tkze.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCh4tkze.png&h=cc5e53c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMORikW.png\" data-thumbn