5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再徒步行兩三公里，<br />\n趕喺S21集中營閂門之前入去。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T22:27:08.000Z","msg":"佢地上網係好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T00:17:26.000Z","msg":"係架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n會唔會太慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc10b2c6782d2638fe724a9a97c1894c464ed1d8","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T00:52:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Day 1 金邊</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[ part 2 ]</span><br />\n<br />\n今日目標好明確，<br />\n就係去<span style=\"color: red;\">S21屠殺集中營</span>，<br />\n-<br />\nToul Sleng 屠殺博物館（又稱S-21)<br />\n原本係一所喺金邊嘅學校，到後來1975紅色高棉統治柬埔寨，將佢改造為集中營同處決中心。<br />\n<br />\n紅色高棉係共產主義政權，奉行毛澤東思想，係短短4年囚押左～15000人，只有7人倖免於難，佢地囚禁知識分子及異見人士，用好多酷刑審問受害者，包括電擊、熱烙、拔掉指甲後倒酒精喺傷口、倒吊完再塞個頭入水等等。館入面展現左好真實嘅環境同相，仲見到少少血跡，啲外國人帶住個語音導航，全部都聽到皺晒眉，你就知道入黎呢度係有幾咁沉重。<br />\n<br />\n好難想像近代歷史有咁唔文明嘅屠殺，但諗諗下，喺呢一刻有個共產國家仍以集中營方式企圖將藏族及維吾爾族洗腦、滅絕佢地嘅文化，仲恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家入到黎S21<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Zew5zq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Zew5zq.png&h=5c656474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先俾大家睇下啲規條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/paD591E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpaD591E.png&h=b7a0d663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第6條真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 成個集中營都圍晒呢啲鐵絲網<br />\n想走都難<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/291LqA9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F291LqA9.png&h=fb499bef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ateX09v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FateX09v.png&h=b16e8f54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQGziWb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQGziWb.png&h=9ec88f93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢舊野係以前學生上PE堂嘅器材<br />\n就俾人拎係倒吊啲犯<br />\n等佢地腦充血失去左意識<br />\n再浸佢地個頭入啲屎水度<br />\n不斷重覆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJ9hgJY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJ9hgJY.png&h=eada9b75&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evgziXk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevgziXk.png&h=13f20112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後再俾大家睇下入面啲相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y93BxiU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY93BxiU.png&h=c4992437&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vu1rUxf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvu1rUxf.png&h=b6559f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BgZkYYf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBgZkYYf.png&h=d3b9031e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qzne3pW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQzne3pW.png&h=dee809d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fF0oWKX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfF0oWKX.png&h=179d8a4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Jxe3pY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Jxe3pY.png&h=df821421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgY2sRE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgY2sRE.png&h=c19c0fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大耐冇食快餐，夜晚去左burgerking<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/25/085111_44b3aa82a340660a45e7624396c8e4e7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F25%2F085111_44b3aa82a340660a45e7624396c8e4e7.png&h=d67ab82c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食左成90蚊，得咁少野食<br />\n<br />\n明天會去Siem reap了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dabd6922b3178fcf956f630f4f2162eeb59f420","tid":993954,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a50e9a51db6934bbcb98a9b356c320638d494cc","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da3729915084c7ed8443ed930a567a19a89e8500","tid":993954,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b18048e2dc569b04d39f3ef9990d982eb4ec989","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Day 1 胡志明 -&gt; 金邊</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[ part 1 ]</span><br />\n<br />\n終於可以離開呢個充滿電單車嘅國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ch4tkze.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCh4tkze.png&h=cc5e53c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMORikW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMORikW.png&h=bf286e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地真係好_煩<br />\n過每一條馬路都令我好攰好攰<br />\n喺馬路都算啦係應該我避你地嘅<br />\n但點解你地要連行人路都唔放過<br />\n你地係咪想迫死我地<br />\n<br />\n今日買左去金邊嘅車飛<br />\n格過價最平大概10USD/230000VND<br />\n大概80蚊，比想像中貴<br />\n呢間叫Kumho，架車都ok<br />\n個司機同個助手都幾nice<br />\n <br />\n成日聽喺柬埔寨過關嗰陣<br />\n啲海關會1蚊1蚊美金咁收你<br />\n係啲下欄錢<br />\n本身整個Visa要30USD（落地簽）<br />\n加埋兩三蚊小費就~33蚊<br />\n但如果你俾司機幫你整，就收你35蚊<br />\n（當然嗰5蚊係袋落自己袋）<br />\n<br />\n本身諗住成車4x人，我地跟大隊<br />\n希望有人可以一齊扺抗司機嘅威迫<br />\n點知，成架車坐得10條友<br />\n個個都乖乖地俾個passport個助手搞<br />\n咁我地可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明知人屈你錢但你咩都做唔到嗰下<br />\n真係好Sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fa2ywBo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffa2ywBo.png&h=1f1eb818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條日本仔<br />\n好似扮聽唔明佢講乜<br />\n之後逃過一劫<br />\n<br />\n胡志明去金邊個陸路關口，叫Bavet<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Hv8kvt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Hv8kvt.png&h=1157110b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知痴乜線<br />\n我竟然夠膽拎部手機出黎影個關口<br />\n好彩冇俾人捉入房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYtRihf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYtRihf.png&h=0f8f13cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身好驚俾完35蚊之後<br />\n又俾海關收多2-3蚊小費<br />\n好彩最後冇事，鬆一口氣<br />\n<br />\n過關嗰陣有人sell sim卡（冇鋪位嗰啲）<br />\n我心諗十幾蚊港紙上唔到咪當跌左<br />\n點知真係上唔到<br />\nsend個wtsapp msg要幾分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uJkwiiD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuJkwiiD.png&h=3f01cd47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過左關再搭多兩個幾鐘車就到金邊<br />\n一落車call左grab tuktuk<br />\n就去左酒店<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KP6n9ra.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKP6n9ra.png&h=806c8bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再徒步行兩三公里，<br />\n趕喺S21集中營閂門之前入去。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T22:27:08.000Z","msg":"佢地上網係好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T00:17:26.000Z","msg":"係架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n會唔會太慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T13:39:04.000Z","msg":"因為我都係用你果個台，你睇下其他區會唔會會好d"},{"pid":"543208b0aa0304735af43d4cabedf6774bad1956","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0dabd6922b3178fcf956f630f4f2162eeb59f420","tid":993954,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a50e9a51db6934bbcb98a9b356c320638d494cc","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da3729915084c7ed8443ed930a567a19a89e8500","tid":993954,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T22:27:08.000Z","msg":"佢地上網係好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T00:17:26.000Z","msg":"係架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n會唔會太慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T13:39:04.000Z","msg":"因為我都係用你果個台，你睇下其他區會唔會會好d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T14:11:05.000Z","msg":"算啦得番兩三日喺度<br />\n酒店房個wifi又正<br />\n當慳番幾蚊美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580558da2f5d63ab02a51791571d5e72a394a521","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T14:27:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Day 2 金邊 -&gt; 暹粒<br />\n[ part 1 ]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日冇乜特別，本身想直接skip，<br />\n但都係係咁2打少少啦。<br />\n<br />\n由於我地兩個都好唔中意大城市，<br />\n又多車又多人交通又亂，<br />\n我地都係決定盡快逃離呢度，<br />\n由金邊坐車去暹粒（~08:00-14:30）。<br />\n<br />\n格左十間八間價，<br />\n巴士價錢個range可以好大，<br />\n由6蚊至15蚊美金不等，<br />\n有成起碼六七間公司，<br />\n我地揀左最平嘅BPA transport。<br />\n買巴士飛記得要格價，<br />\n價錢可以差好遠，<br />\n（搵Hostel一定係貴）<br />\n最緊要係你問完唔買呢度都冇人會西你面。<br />\n<br />\n本身仲驚冇冷氣，<br />\nturn out架巴士真係幾ok，<br />\n冷氣又夠，司機都揸得幾安全，<br />\n成車坐得十條友。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/25/222309_44197d87072fae0695aa5293adfbce24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F25%2F222309_44197d87072fae0695aa5293adfbce24.png&h=e3b1d7b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/25/222351_b98a14165f26bd8c5dbca2db7e2a5324.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F25%2F222351_b98a14165f26bd8c5dbca2db7e2a5324.png&h=750e177f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後會打下晏晝夜晚食左啲乜，<br />\n都係啲平民野，唔好有咩期望。<br />\n（自問唔係食家，亦唔係豪遊，<br />\n所以普遍都係求其揀啲平民野食就算）"},{"pid":"9890aa9ec32734f7348bf805d83979909558ef2a","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Day 2 金邊 -&gt; 暹粒<br />\n[ part 2 ]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">介紹少少Siem reap嘅野食<br />\n1. Coffee Shop Noodle - 甜湯牛河</span><br />\n<br />\n首先想講自己食野嘅preference<br />\n等你地有個參考<br />\n我本身係好中意食肉同重口味野<br />\n都幾中意食辣<br />\n又中意食煎炸野<br />\n總之唔健康嘅我都中意食<br />\n希望唔好咁快大腸癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係葱、芫茜、西芹<br />\n太重味嗰啲香料eg 薄荷葉<br />\n都係好抗拒。<br />\n<br />\n至於價錢方面<br />\n我甚少豪飲豪食<br />\n而我亦都唔算好咀刁<br />\n總之扺食對我黎講係好緊要<br />\n最緊要性價比高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一間想介紹嘅係食牛河嘅<br />\n叫Coffee noodle soup<br />\n想知喺邊自己可以google下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07RvOJK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07RvOJK.png&h=6fd24429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間野都Google都有4.7分<br />\n唔算位於市中心<br />\n但喺burger king行3-5分鐘就到<br />\n<br />\n間野唔係好好坐俾你入去chill嗰啲<br />\n但都幾乾淨<br />\n野食方面其實都係得幾樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vm23pjf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvm23pjf.png&h=134b5c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過最值得提嘅係<br />\n呢度個湯真係好甜<br />\n同其他牛河鋪頭唔同<br />\n佢係Sell個湯係冇用肉黎煲<br />\n全素菜，冇味精<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xvwopka.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxvwopka.png&h=4cc482ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n碗野就係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7iuj1C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7iuj1C.png&h=ea734160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n價值美金2蚊<br />\n凍咖啡就五毫，超濃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGG38Vy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGG38Vy.png&h=a3bd7aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我黎左食兩次，兩次都清晒<br />\n<br />\n仲有不得不提<br />\n老闆娘非常有善。<br />\n<br />\n其中有一個缺點<br />\n就係要等得比較耐<br />\n可能因為所有野都係即刻整。<br />\n<br />\n我望住個廚房，<br />\n睇得出佢地好用心去煮每一碗麵，<br />\n有興趣又經過嘅可以黎try try<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76945c29f2e20768f9f90f187d3b129b87c0127c","tid":993954,"uid":206737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"支持，一路追"},{"pid":"d508db86641dfac9b5c3485a35f6d3080abb9626","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76945c29f2e20768f9f90f187d3b129b87c0127c","tid":993954,"uid":206737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"支持，一路追"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T16:21:38.000Z","msg":"好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThz bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81e6b7bc191fe262d27a09419aa72b00c4c67aa","tid":993954,"uid":206737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:28:43.000Z","msg":"碗牛河，望落好正"},{"pid":"8265ccd354398d15051a88f96b5a61f0a5b33fa8","tid":993954,"uid":76263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"想問下金邊值唔值得去三日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b420d7a3e3f661b4c2b96c3b4ac5c7fc7eb976","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8265ccd354398d15051a88f96b5a61f0a5b33fa8","tid":993954,"uid":76263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"想問下金邊值唔值得去三日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:00:09.000Z","msg":"三日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就覺得唔值<br />\n冇乜特別嘅景點<br />\n係都係夾硬搵景點去eg 紀念碑<br />\n純粹一個比暹粒嘅大城市"},{"pid":"9259868a9ff16a4aa86fe64ea63fa097f01f39a8","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:46:54.000Z","msg":"都係唔跟次序打<br />\n因為個行程都冇乜特別<br />\n人人黎吳哥窟多數都係跟個3日tour<br />\n之後會再詳細少少講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢篇想再介紹多少少野食先<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n明明我乜狗屎垃圾都話好食<br />\n唔知做乜做走出黎介紹野食<br />\n不過都想分享多幾樣柬國美食<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: violet;\">Amok 呀莫</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKb4hdV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKb4hdV.png&h=754a4142&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NUfMvyW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNUfMvyW.png&h=94a37d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢兩碟，個人覺得係柬國菜no.1<br />\n係廚師嘔出黎嘅嘔吐物<br />\n個賣相都真係幾似<br />\n但其實係超重椰汁味嘅？咖哩<br />\n仲有好多香料，但唔會難入口<br />\n（可能我本身中意食咖哩所以好中意食）<br />\n食落有好多煮爛晒嘅菜<br />\n加埋啲肉（建議揀魚，會去晒骨），<br />\n用佢撈飯真係一流<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"color: violet;\">Lok Lak beef</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q1vkz2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq1vkz2b.png&h=4e4cb5f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WLvMvAx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWLvMvAx.png&h=d672ed89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡單講即係甜酸牛肉<br />\n好開胃<br />\n唔算好特別但都值得一試<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: violet;\">Khmer Red curry</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WGf8J44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWGf8J44.png&h=041f72e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個都係比較重椰汁味<br />\n一啲都唔辣<br />\n都係香料比較多<br />\n但唔算好特別<br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: violet;\">街邊炒公仔麵</span><br />\n<br />\n一開始好好奇呢啲車仔係咪關東煮<br />\n再加個麵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KDVoXb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KDVoXb.png&h=322e48f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行近睇原來有部分車仔係炒麵<br />\n部分係冾<br />\n認住呢個呀叔<br />\n佢炒得勁_好食，又有鑊氣<br />\n完全同香港茶餐廳嗰啲乜乜炒一丁差幾皮<br />\n（喺香港冇乜食過好食嘅炒公仔麵）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXFphhe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXFphhe.png&h=f5fb292d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有落蒜蓉、少少辣椒醬、糖、等等<br />\n再加啲菜，煎隻蛋，就食得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YpNyU3X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYpNyU3X.png&h=89f5a56f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n埋單1蚊美金<br />\n我食過第二間有埋牛肉都係1蚊<br />\n不過冇咁好食<br />\n<br />\n認住呢間40號車仔<br />\n我問個大叔：you always stay here？<br />\n（佢心諗：係咪真係好食到要追住我）<br />\n大叔：No，everywhere<br />\n<br />\n佢地係揸住架電單車嘅流動鋪頭<br />\n所以會周圍走<br />\n好似啲聖獸咁難捉<br />\n聽講捉齊晒就可以上太空<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5B8VoXi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5B8VoXi.png&h=7e6be261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我食過一次之後，就冇再見過佢了<br />\n<br />\n5. 生果方面<br />\n我都推薦菠蘿同芒果<br />\n超甜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/27/224049_3c0210ed44a0a300960b361409a7b89b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F224049_3c0210ed44a0a300960b361409a7b89b.png&h=5e8f4933&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺女王宮都1美金兩袋<br />\n我估出面可以更平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我呢幾日食過幾間柬埔寨餐廳<br />\n當然完全冇食過貴野<br />\nPub street嗰啲餐廳屬於貴價<br />\n每個飯都~4-5USD<br />\n我都覺得貴<br />\n所以永遠只入2-3蚊一個飯嘅餐廳<br />\n其實佢地啲餐廳（唔似香港嗰啲）<br />\n你是但入一間，其實都係好食<br />\n<br />\n不過如果想試嘅<br />\n可以搵下<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">The palm cafe</span><br />\n平得黎又好食都算ok乾淨<br />\n食佢個Amok，包保你快樂"},{"pid":"00c143068e9fbb52040de271bffda9e4cfc0a307","tid":993954,"uid":214367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T20:35:44.000Z","msg":"有無食囡囡"},{"pid":"1e5437e0e61e0c35e5561f23da3a4238afa0790d","tid":993954,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T21:42:27.000Z","msg":"佢地d肉完全唔得，超鞋"},{"pid":"a8df405f11721e98db0a2c1117633a5170e1d598","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00c143068e9fbb52040de271bffda9e4cfc0a307","tid":993954,"uid":214367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T20:35:44.000Z","msg":"有無食囡囡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:28:11.000Z","msg":"柬妹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好咩<br />\n同越南妹好唔同<br />\n柬妹黑啲純樸啲但Pure啲"},{"pid":"15f888a2df290826df4271dc7994bd1de47763ac","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e5437e0e61e0c35e5561f23da3a4238afa0790d","tid":993954,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T21:42:27.000Z","msg":"佢地d肉完全唔得，超鞋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:06:40.000Z","msg":"我都覺<br />\n所有肉都係咁<br />\n又鞋又韌<br />\n得魚最好食<br />\n所以Amok一定要揀魚"},{"pid":"6bebf26c79333d23c2a54883aed96c6b8bcb4da9","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:23:39.000Z","msg":"之後到打下<span style=\"color: red;\">吳哥窒行程</span><br />\n多數人都會黎玩三日<br />\n除左啲大陸人，淨係玩一日<br />\n（會出沒喺啲最出名嘅景點）<br />\n<br />\n三日行程多數分為<br />\n1. 細圈<br />\n- <span style=\"color: green;\">小吳哥</span><br />\n- <span style=\"color: green;\">Ta Phrom</span>（樹屋）拍Tomb raider嗰度<br />\n- <span style=\"color: green;\">Bayon</span>（高棉的微笑）<br />\n入面個area好大<br />\n- 巴肯山看日落<br />\n- Ta keo<br />\n- Banteay Kdei<br />\n<br />\n2. 大圈<br />\n- 小吳哥看日出<br />\n- <span style=\"color: green;\">Pre Rup</span><br />\n- <span style=\"color: green;\">Ta som</span><br />\n- East Mebon<br />\n- <span style=\"color: green;\">Neak Pean</span><br />\n- Preah Khan<br />\n<br />\n3. 外圈<br />\n- <span style=\"color: green;\">女皇宮</span><br />\n- Roluos site<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">Bakong</span>，神牛寺<br />\n- Beng Mealea（另付5蚊入場費）<br />\n- Tonle Sap Lake（每人<span style=\"color: red;\">25</span>USD船票）<br />\n<br />\n上面<span style=\"color: green;\">綠色字即係我建議要去</span><br />\n<br />\n一般三日行程都係大同小異<br />\n我睇完個blog見個人評價唔錯<br />\n就搵左佢<br />\n2日tuktuk（大細圈），1日私家車（外圈）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bGFQhvQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbGFQhvQ.png&h=3b057dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總共95蚊美金<br />\n包：<br />\n- 機場接送<br />\n（不過我地搭細規模嘅巴士公司佢話佢唔知我地喺邊落車所以冇黎接）<br />\n- 巴肯山日落<br />\n- 小吳哥日出<br />\n- Tonle Sap日落<br />\n<br />\n由於好多temple都太似<br />\n我都唔會詳細續個作介紹<br />\n（事實係我都冇乜做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n晏啲會Post下啲相<br />\n<br />\n（本身一路去緊吳哥窟就一路期待mingjai會可以點樣拍得好有趣，點知比起其他系列我覺得比較遜色。我覺得佢剪同拍嗰時其實同我宜家打遊記都有少少相似，就係因為3日嘅行程都太相似，所以都冇乜好多野以打到拍到。佢個外圈同大圈都合埋變左同一日）"},{"pid":"7c040ff3537e9fbc3bef27c0948cab4cac490af1","tid":993954,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15f888a2df290826df4271dc7994bd1de47763ac","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e5437e0e61e0c35e5561f23da3a4238afa0790d","tid":993954,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T21:42:27.000Z","msg":"佢地d肉完全唔得，超鞋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:06:40.000Z","msg":"我都覺<br />\n所有肉都係咁<br />\n又鞋又韌<br />\n得魚最好食<br />\n所以Amok一定要揀魚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:23:58.000Z","msg":"菜 水果都好新鮮"},{"pid":"10d2b06a81decf569ca5d60b38c81befc67dc0f1","tid":993954,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8df405f11721e98db0a2c1117633a5170e1d598","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00c143068e9fbb52040de271bffda9e4cfc0a307","tid":993954,"uid":214367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T20:35:44.000Z","msg":"有無食囡囡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:28:11.000Z","msg":"柬妹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好咩<br />\n同越南妹好唔同<br />\n柬妹黑啲純樸啲但Pure啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"可能太曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢地好多中小學生就出黎做野"},{"pid":"cf0b8483afd88ad6e3c54e492079b5adc543da5f","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10d2b06a81decf569ca5d60b38c81befc67dc0f1","tid":993954,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8df405f11721e98db0a2c1117633a5170e1d598","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00c143068e9fbb52040de271bffda9e4cfc0a307","tid":993954,"uid":214367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T20:35:44.000Z","msg":"有無食囡囡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:28:11.000Z","msg":"柬妹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好咩<br />\n同越南妹好唔同<br />\n柬妹黑啲純樸啲但Pure啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"可能太曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢地好多中小學生就出黎做野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:56:25.000Z","msg":"可能幫補家計掛<br />\n又可能冇諗咁長遠，<br />\n覺得賺錢緊要過讀書。<br />\n<br />\n不過同個司機傾過，<br />\n呢度小學同初中都免費，<br />\n但唔係強制要返學。<br />\n<br />\n政府唔理你地返唔返學，<br />\n唔返仲好，<br />\n佢地慳番啲錢自己袋落袋。"},{"pid":"f13361240a52ca9f4726d30744ad632c1a4b4cbb","tid":993954,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:09:54.000Z","msg":"不得不提嘅係<br />\n吳哥窒已經被大陸人攻佔<br />\n同我5年前黎已經好唔同了<br />\n一入到去勁多普通話<br />\n勁大聲勁有高低起伏起卷利<br />\n我以為自己去左世界之窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔可以靜靜地欣賞下呢度<br />\n嘈到Hihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾佢地搞到勁燥底<br />\n成日同啲鬼佬鬼婆對望<br />\n好無奈咁苦笑<br />\n都會好希望佢地識分中國同香港人<br />\n<br />\n仲要佢地個個都著到成隻女鬼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁多<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span>長裙<br />\n再唔係就係啲<span style=\"color: violet;\">粉紅</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">青色</span><br />\n完全係一細個人就會完全破壞左張相<br />\n<br />\n特別多大陸人嘅地方：<br />\n吳哥寺、Bayon、巴肯山日落<br />\n<br />\n至於大圈同外圈，相對上會少啲大陸人<br />\n可以靜靜地喺啲寺入面休息下"}]}